"title": "6606: access to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6606",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The privilege of entering into the presence of God through the work of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Only the pure have access to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:21-1John3:22\">1JN 3:21–3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:12\">PSA 41:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:18-Ps66:19\">PSA 66:18–66:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:28\">PSA 73:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:12\">1PE 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:15-Ps34:16\">PSA 34:15–34:16</a></p>\n<h2>The wicked do not have access to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:7\">PSA 101:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:2\">ISA 59:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:14\">GEN 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:16\">GEN 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:3\">LEV 22:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:18\">DEU 31:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:5\">PSA 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:7\">ISA 64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:15\">JER 7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:1\">JER 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:39\">JER 23:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:3\">JER 52:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:23\">EZK 39:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:6\">HOS 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:4\">MIC 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Access to God through the priests and sacrificial system</h2>\n<h3>Access to God by this means in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:44-Exod29:45\">EXO 29:44–29:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:29-Exod29:30\">EXO 29:29–29:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:36\">EXO 29:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:38-Exod29:39\">EXO 29:38–29:39</a></p>\n<h3>This OT access to God fulfilled in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:14-Heb4:16\">HEB 4:14–4:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:23-Heb7:25\">HEB 7:23–7:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17\">HEB 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:18-Heb7:19\">HEB 7:18–7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10-Heb10:12\">HEB 10:10–10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:18-Heb12:24\">HEB 12:18–12:24</a></p>\n<h3>Access to God by the priesthood of all believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:6\">REV 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Access to God through the Tent of Meeting and the tabernacle</h2>\n<h3>Access to God by this means in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:7-Exod33:11\">EXO 33:7–33:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:1-Exod40:2\">EXO 40:1–40:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:35\">EXO 40:34–40:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:51\">NUM 1:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:10\">NUM 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:38\">NUM 3:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:7\">NUM 18:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:22\">NUM 18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:3\">2CH 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>This OT access to God fulfilled in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:23-Heb9:24\">HEB 9:23–9:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:44\">ACT 7:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:1-Heb8:2\">HEB 8:1–8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:5-Heb8:6\">HEB 8:5–8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:11\">HEB 9:11</a></p>\n<h2>Access to God through the Most Holy Place</h2>\n<h3>Access to God by this means in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:7-Heb9:8\">HEB 9:7–9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:2\">LEV 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:12-Lev16:17\">LEV 16:12–16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:32-Lev16:33\">LEV 16:32–16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:16\">1KI 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:6\">1KI 8:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:7\">2CH 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:11\">1KI 8:10–8:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13-2Chr5:14\">2CH 5:13–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:8\">2CH 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Access to God by this means fulfilled in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:3-Heb9:5\">HEB 9:3–9:5</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:12\">HEB 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:22\">HEB 10:19–10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:51\">MAT 27:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:38\">MRK 15:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:19-Heb6:20\">HEB 6:19–6:20</a></p>\n<h2>Believers have access to God by grace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:6\">PSA 21:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:10-Ps51:11\">PSA 51:10–51:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:18\">PSA 145:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:1-Hos6:2\">HOS 6:1–6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:27\">ACT 17:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h2>Believers have access to God through Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:2\">ROM 5:1–5:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:18\">EPH 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:12\">EPH 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:9\">JHN 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a></p>",
